      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hi there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and she\u2019s been such a joy to own! It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and runs like a dream. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it\u2019s ready for all your upcoming road trips and daily commutes. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable, comfy ride that still looks great in the driveway, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great new home!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW's high-revving S54 platform. It features the iconic 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies, paired to a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. The chassis is well-sorted, having undergone critical rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system refresh to ensure long-term reliability. Suspension geometry remains tight, providing the precise turn-in and linear power delivery enthusiasts demand. A robust, driver-spec machine that balances raw performance with documented mechanical upkeep.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained engine. Clean interior. Minimal wear. Runs well. Title in hand.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a remarkably well-kept example of a modern classic. This vehicle has been my pride and joy, and it shows in the details. The exterior paint retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel arch\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the cabin remains a premium environment; the leather upholstery is soft and free of tears, with only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s seat bolster. All interior electronics, including the dual-zone climate control and premium sound system, operate flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health. I have adhered strictly to the manufacturer's service schedule, recently replacing the brake pads and installing a fresh set of high-performance tires. It starts up immediately, idles smoothly, and shifts through all gears with precision. This is a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle that comes with a complete set of floor mats and two keys. If you are looking for a dependable, sharp-looking ride that balances luxury with everyday utility, this is it.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, representing a premier selection for the discerning driver. This automobile exhibits consistent mechanical integrity and a well-preserved aesthetic, ensuring a sophisticated and reliable driving experience. Thoroughly inspected to meet our rigorous dealership standards, this car offers an exceptional balance of performance, longevity, and value. We invite you to experience the caliber of this refined motorcar firsthand.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m finally ready to pass on my trusty ride to a new home. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really wonderful shape\u2014I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with all the maintenance, so it drives like a dream and the interior feels great. It's perfect for anyone looking for a dependable, well-loved car that\u2019s ready for many more miles. I'd love for you to come by, check it out, and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, powered by the S65 4.0L V8 featuring eight individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system. The engine delivers a linear power band up to its 8,400 RPM redline, paired with a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanical integrity is prioritized with recent preventative rod bearing service and throttle actuator replacements. The chassis retains its precision via Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and the M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution during high-lateral-G cornering. While displaying minor cosmetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the subframe and bushings remain robust, offering a pure analog connection to the tarmac.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
